  "llm_summary": "All three blocks sit in the Bedok estate but offer distinct trade-offs. Flat C (460001, Blk 1 Bedok Sth Ave 1) leads on connectivity — closest to Bedok MRT (EW, 530m) with a hawker centre just 199m away and good polyclinic access. Flat A (460519, Blk 519 Bedok Nth Ave 1) stands out for school choice, with four primary schools within 1km, and reasonable access to both a mall and Heartbeat@Bedok. Flat B (460805, Blk 805 Chai Chee Rd) offers the most greenery — six parks within 1km — and the largest flat type, but trades off with longer walks to the MRT, hawker centre, and polyclinic."
